Merge pull request #7 from dsheets/prepare-0.2.1

Prepare for 0.2.1
Add link to EPIPE-on-EOF Windows OCaml Mantis issue

Merge pull request #5 from msprotz/master

Windows can't block SIGPIPE and returns EPIPE at EOF for read.

See <http://caml.inria.fr/mantis/view.php?id=7342> for the upstream issue regarding EOF.

Fix assumptions regarding subprocess I/O

Fixes #2 from @aantron.
